<li><a href="$(HOME)/security/2004/dsa-433">Linux 2.4.17</a> (mips+mipsel) --
    Local root exploit.
<li><a href="$(HOME)/security/2004/dsa-434">gaim</a> --
    Several vulnerabilities.
</ul>

